br />\neg 4:3 2.35:1<br />\n佢將其他常見比例concentric<br />\n框出黎個結果就約莫係16:9<br />\n咁做個好處係啲舊片只要加黑邊就播到<br />\n而唔洗改條片長寬比例 <br />\n<br />\n之後做咗國際標準 就全世界都跟佢<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇落幾合理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:29:52.000Z","msg":"睇多少少<br />\n佢有講本身03-08年興16:10 近黃金比例<br />\n不過之後因為效益高啲轉16:9"},{"pid":"daa048f346440e52ab4071fd396cc171d7222a71","tid":2361573,"uid":148778,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"874f4a5095312e323d1eba1c4ab3f112996cfaee","tid":2361573,"uid":143411,"like":6,"dislike":27,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T19:21:54.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T05:04:43.000Z","msg":"討論區唔俾討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e39af0a82523ceac5179376063f438b854bd943","tid":2361573,"uid":79851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2bac473b7a176a9cb6c93ee73540d247e940bbc","tid":2361573,"uid":350157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T20:00:07.000Z","msg":"黃金比例啫係幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:29:07.000Z","msg":"1:1.619"},{"pid":"99369270872f63a8e47c25e028a5d29c6bd35f85","tid":2361573,"uid":92906,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:35:21.000Z","msg":"兒登原來唔係冇原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好負評住<br />\n真心由古時講起<br />\n<br />\n16:9 取用最大原因係一統電視，電腦，以至後來手機既各種media 而成<br />\n<br />\n中間既16:10 21:9比較專為電腦同打機而設，難成氣候<br />\n<br />\n除左用家角度，應該要了解埋數碼化高清年代既相機，以至電視台/電影業界拍攝器材ccd既比例<br />\n<br />\n有玩開相機影音既就唔難明白<br />\n16:9的確係呢廿年間各種比例中市佔率既高既比例<br />\n<br />\n30年前日本hdtv 既高清制式已經一早定左16:9 , 與當年電影既比例睇齊，呢個過渡一早出玩左，並唔係近1x年既事"}],"pinned":{"pid":"40b00a21918687749e0d04c01d9bac8ae6437bc2","tid":2361573,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bPx6mS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\